Class:        Amphibia
Habitat:      Lakes
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     15 years
Weight:       0.3 kg
Status:       Critically Endangered
Fact:         Can regenerate entire limbs, spine, heart, and brain tissue

Name:         Octopus
Scientific:   Octopus vulgaris
Class:        Cephalopoda
Habitat:      Ocean
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     3 years
Weight:       10 kg
Status:       Least Concern
Fact:         3 hearts, blue blood; changes color in 0.3 seconds; 9 brains

Name:         Peregrine Falcon
Scientific:   Falco peregrinus
Class:        Aves
Habitat:      Cliffs/Cities
Diet:         Carnivore
